title: Ep. 136 - At The Polls, Remember Kavanaugh
description:
As we head into the election, Democrats are really hoping you forget about their failed smear campaign against an innocent man. I'll talk about why you shouldn't. Also, we'll discuss SNL's mockery of a wounded vet, and I will offer a defense of a teacher arrested for assaulting a student. Date: 11-05-2018
